'''林達博共振'''的名稱源自瑞典星系天文學家[[貝蒂爾·林德布拉德|貝蒂·林達博]]<ref>{{cite book
|title=Galactic dynamics (Princeton series in astrophysics)
|first1=James
|last1=Binney
|first2=Scott
|last2=Tremaine
|publisher=Princeton University Press
|year=1988
|isbn=0-691-08445-9
|page=149
|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=01yNf7mipb0C}}, [http://books.google.com/books?id=01yNf7mipb0C&pg=PA149 Chapter 3, p. 149]
</ref>，是天體的[[周轉頻率|周轉頻率]]（其中一個的[[拱點|拱點]]與另一個成比率）有著簡單和複合的[[諧振|強制頻率]]的一種[[軌道共振|軌道共振]]。種共振傾向於增加天體的[[軌道離心率|軌道離心率]]<ref>{{cite book
|title=Numerical astrophysics: proceedings of the International Conference on Numerical Astrophysics 1998 (NAP98)
|first1=Shoken M.
|last1=Miyama
|first2=Kohji
|last2=Tomisaka
|first3=Tomoyuki
|last3=Hanawa
|publisher=Springer
|year=1999
|isbn=0-792-3556-6
|page=162
|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=9mvhdGS8nCAC}}, [http://books.google.com/books?id=9mvhdGS8nCAC&pg=PA162 Page 162]
</ref>，和造成它的[[近心點經度|拱點經度]]與強制力的一致性。林達博共振導出了[[密度波理論|螺旋密度波]]<ref>{{cite book
|title=Star formation in the interstellar medium: in honor of David Hollenbach, Chris McKee, and Frank Shu
|first1=D.
|last1=Johnstone
|publisher=Astronomical Society of the Pa
|year=2004
|isbn=1-58381-185-0
|page=73
|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=RpDvAAAAMAAJ}}, [http://books.google.com/books?id=RpDvAAAAMAAJ&q=%22Lindblad+resonances%22+drive+spiral+%22density+waves%22 Snippet page 73 ]
</ref>，不僅適用在[[星系|星系]]（恆星是受螺旋臂本身的[[諧振|力]]支配），也適用於[[土星環|土星環]]（環中的微粒是受到[[土星的衛星|土星衛星]]的力支配）。 

林達博共振影響了恆星與[[星系盤|星系盤]]中心的距離，恆星軌道速度的徑向分量的自然頻率與其經過的螺旋臂的重力位能最大值的頻率接近。如果恆星環繞星系中心的軌道速度大於它將經過這一部份螺旋臂的速度，則將發生內林達博共振－如果相似，則是外林達博共振<ref>{{cite book
|title=The Physics of Astrophysics: Gas dynamics
|first1=Frank H.
|last1=Shu
|publisher=University Science Books
|year=1992
|isbn=0-935702-65-2
|page=147
|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=50VYSc56URUC}}, [http://books.google.com/books?id=50VYSc56URUC&pg=PA147 Chapter 11, p. 147]
</ref>。處於內林達博共振，恆星的軌道速度將會增加，使恆星向外移動；而處於外林達博共振則會降低軌道速度，造成恆星向內運動。

